FBIS4-11950 "drnes064_a_94006" FBIS-NES-94-064 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Other Arrests Noted Other Arrests Noted LD0204201894 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 2 Apr 94 LD0204201894 Algiers ENTV Television Network Arabic BFN [Text] In a statement by the security authorities it was announced today that the security forces had liquidated 37 terrorists between Wednesday and Friday, and arrested another 62 between Monday and Thursday in different areas of the nation. The security authorities also announced that a mujahid had been assassinated in the village of Ergen in Jijel Province. A terrorist group had also set fire to Souk El Fellah in the agricultural village of Bouchahhar in Tipaza Province. The security authorities statement adds that another terrorist group in Tipaza dug up and wrecked the Sidi Abdelkader cemetery. Armed men also stormed an elementary school in the municipality of Babour, Setif Province, and tore up the national flag.
